# MiePyScatt
Gaugain Gabriel (gabriel.gaugain@univ-rennes1.fr)

Implementation of the Mie scattering theory for incident electromagnetic plane wave on a (dielectric) sphere.
All the calculation are based on the following theoretical book:

[1]C. F. Bohren et D. R. Huffman, Absorption and Scattering of Light by Small Particles, 1ʳᵉ éd. Wiley, 1998.


